msgstr "使用这个主题来帮助您通过 Windows PowerShell 管理 Windows 和 Windows Server 技术。"

msgid "# Repair-ClusterStorageSpacesDirect"
msgstr "# 修复直接访问集群存储空间的问题"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid "Repairs disks in a Storage Spaces Direct (S2D) system."
msgstr "修复Storage Spaces Direct（S2D）系统中的磁盘。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "### DefaultParameterSet (Default)"
msgstr "### DefaultParameterSet（默认值）"

msgid "### SkipDiskRecoverySet"
msgstr "### SkipDiskRecoverySet"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The `Repair-ClusterStorageSpacesDirect` cmdlet repairs Storage Spaces Direct"
" (S2D) disks."
msgstr ""
"`Repair-ClusterStorageSpacesDirect` cmdlet 用于修复 Storage Spaces Direct (S2D) "
"磁盘。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Repair S2D on all nodes"
msgstr "### 示例 1：修复所有节点上的 S2D 系统"

msgid "This command repairs S2D on all nodes without user confirmation."
msgstr "此命令会在所有节点上修复S2D问题，而无需用户确认。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet as a background job. Use this parameter to run commands that take a long time to\n"
"complete."
msgstr "以后台作业的方式运行该cmdlet。使用此参数来执行需要较长时间才能完成的命令。"

msgid ""
"The cmdlet immediately returns an object that represents the job and then displays the command\n"
"prompt. You can continue to work in the session while the job completes. To manage the job, use the\n"
"`*-Job` cmdlets. To get the job results, use the\n"
"[Receive-Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"该cmdlet会立即返回一个表示该作业的对象，然后显示命令提示符。在作业完成之前，您可以继续在该会话中工作。要管理该作业，请使用`*-Job`系列的cmdlets；要获取作业结果，请使用[Receive-"
"Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"For more information about Windows PowerShell background jobs, see\n"
"[about_Jobs](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)."
msgstr ""
"有关 Windows PowerShell 后台作业的更多信息，请参阅 "
"[关于作业](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet in a remote session or on a remote computer. Enter a computer name or a session\n"
"object, such as the output of a [New-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)\n"
"or [Get-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet. The default is the\n"
"current session on the local computer."
msgstr ""
"在远程会话或远程计算机上运行该 cmdlet。请输入一个计算机名称或会话对象（例如 `[New-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)` 或 `[Get-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966)` cmdlet "
"的输出结果）。默认值是本地计算机上的当前会话。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行 cmdlet 之前会提示您进行确认。"

msgid ""
"Indicates that this cmdlet disables storage maintenance mode. You can use this parameter to clean\n"
"the storage maintenance mode setting on physical disks."
msgstr "表示此 cmdlet 会禁用存储维护模式。您可以使用该参数来清除物理磁盘上的存储维护模式设置。"

msgid ""
"Specifies a node on which the cmdlet performs the operation. If you don't specify a value, all\n"
"nodes are used."
msgstr "指定一个节点，cmdlet将在该节点上执行操作。如果您不指定值，则会使用所有节点。"

msgid ""
"Indicates that this cmdlet recovers physical disks that are unbound. This parameter can be used when\n"
"disks are reported to be in a lost communication state. When this parameter is specified, S2D\n"
"attempts to reestablish the binding between disks in slow and fast tiers, making disks accessible\n"
"again."
msgstr ""
"表示此 cmdlet 可恢复未绑定的物理磁盘。当有磁盘被报告处于“通信中断”状态时，可以使用该参数。指定此参数后，S2D "
"会尝试重新建立慢速层和快速层之间的磁盘绑定关系，从而使这些磁盘再次可访问。"

msgid ""
"Indicates that this cmdlet recovers disks so they can be reevaluated to be claimed when repairing\n"
"Storage Spaces Direct."
msgstr "表示此 cmdlet 可恢复磁盘，以便在修复 Storage Spaces Direct 时重新评估是否可以将其回收使用。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the maximum number of concurrent operations that can be established to run the cmdlet. If\n"
"this parameter is omitted or a value of `0` is entered, then Windows PowerShell calculates an\n"
"optimum throttle limit for the cmdlet based on the number of CIM cmdlets that are running on the\n"
"computer. The throttle limit applies only to the current cmdlet, not to the session or to the\n"
"computer."
msgstr ""
"该参数用于指定可以同时运行的 cmdlet 操作的最大数量。如果省略此参数或输入值 `0`，则 Windows PowerShell "
"会根据计算机上正在运行的 CIM cmdlet 的数量来计算该 cmdlet 的最佳限制值。此限制仅适用于当前正在运行的 "
"cmdlet，而不适用于整个会话或计算机本身。"

msgid "Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs. The cmdlet isn't run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上并没有运行这个cmdlet。"

msgid "### CommonParameters"
msgstr "### CommonParameters"

msgid ""
"This cmdlet supports the common parameters: -Debug, -ErrorAction, -ErrorVariable,\n"
"-InformationAction, -InformationVariable, -OutVariable, -OutBuffer, -PipelineVariable, -Verbose,\n"
"-WarningAction, and -WarningVariable. For more information, see\n"
"[about_CommonParameters](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113216)."
msgstr ""
"此 cmdlet "
"支持以下常见参数：-Debug、-ErrorAction、-ErrorVariable、-InformationAction、-OutputVariable、-OutBuffer、-PipelineVariable、-Verbose、-WarningAction"
" 和 -WarningVariable。有关更多信息，请参阅 "
"[关于通用参数](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113216)。"

